item.title: How to Position Yourself for Promotion | Episode 91
item.description: Every man wants to go to the next level in their walk with God, purpose, and Kingdom assignment. In this episode we cover a fundamental of how to position yourself for promotion. Many men are in conflict with themselves, and because they are out of alignment in this area, they stay stuck in their current circumstances and fail to advance into their next assignment... item.title: "The 4th Quarter"| 3rd Podcast Anniversary Series| Dennis McNulty| Pastor of LFWC | Head Coach: Timothy Christian School Boys' Basketball
item.description:
The Servant Leader Coaches Bible Study is celebrating and thanking God for 3 years!! We present a series with the theme: "The 4th Quarter: How to Serve for the Return of Christ." We will be joined by various Servant Leaders.

Dennis Mculty is no stranger to the podcast. He is the Pastor of Lighthouse Family Worship Center and the Head Boys Basketball Coach at Timothy Christian School in New Jersey.
